{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Nr6YStbX4X2MCGNX9gy52Z","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Prometheus service maps port 8000 → 9090 (the container). The Prometheus deployment uses `--web.enable-lifecycle` so I can call `POST /-/reload` on the Prometheus internal port 9090 to reload config.\n\nNow let me update the ConfigMap to add RabbitMQ scrape targets using the headless service. The headless service `rabbitmq-headless` gives DNS resolution to individual pods:\n- rabbitmq-0.rabbitmq-headless.{ns}.svc.cluster.local:15692\n- rabbitmq-1.rabbitmq-headless.{ns}.svc.cluster.local:15692\n- rabbitmq-2.rabbitmq-headless.{ns}.svc.cluster.local:15692\n\nRabbitMQ exposes metrics at `/metrics` on port 15692. The existing config already has the correct `localhost:9090` target for Prometheus to scrape itself, so I just need to add the RabbitMQ targets to the ConfigMap.\n\nSince `--web.enable-lifecycle` is enabled, I can update the ConfigMap and then exec into the Prometheus pod to trigger a config reload via the lifecycle endpoint rather than restarting the entire pod.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":781,"cache_read_input_tokens":33331,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":781},"output_tokens":32,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"20298e0f-8e64-4228-b512-2c4dbd1aac31","uuid":"8edd9727-2145-4160-acc8-d19170e7a8cf","request_id":"req_011CcQ5QCJoK7ocdrDQWYRfx"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Nr6YStbX4X2MCGNX9gy52Z","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue is clear: Prometheus config only scrapes `localhost:9090` — no RabbitMQ targets. I'll update the ConfigMap to add all 3 RabbitMQ pods via the headless service, then trigger a hot reload."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":781,"cache_read_input_tokens":33331,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":781},"output_tokens":32,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"20298e0f-8e64-4228-b512-2c4dbd1aac31","uuid":"910327d2-97fd-423f-98c6-4c3b03c7cead","request_id":"req_011CcQ5QCJoK7ocdrDQWYRfx"}
